OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773090363
OL,3,CDurham's Milburngate complex sold to
OL,4,Cprivate company
OL,6,FDurham County Council has announced
OL,7,Fthe sale of the Milburngate leisure
OL,8,Fcomplex in Durham after years of
OL,9,Funcertainty.
OL,11,FThe six-acre site on Durham's
OL,12,Friverside was due to be completed in
OL,13,F2022 but has remained unfinished and
OL,14,Fempty, raising questions about its
OL,15,Flong-term future.
OL,17,FNorthold Group, which has acquired the
OL,18,Fsite, says its plans include a
OL,19,Fboutique cinema, new restaurants and
OL,20,Fbars and a hotel.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
