OL,3,CDurham's Milburngate complex sold to
OL,4,Cprivate company
OL,6,FNorthhold Group, has acquired
OL,7,FMilburngate in Durham, a six-acre
OL,8,Fmixed-use entertainment, workspace and
OL,9,Fresidential development.
OL,11,FIn a statement, it said: "We are
OL,12,Fexcited to move forward and bring this
OL,13,Flandmark development to completion.
OL,14,FMilburngate represents a significant
OL,15,Fopportunity for Durham, and we look
OL,16,Fforward to working collaboratively
OL,17,Fwith all stakeholders, including
OL,18,FDurham County Council, to deliver a
OL,19,Fvibrant and successful destination for
OL,20,Fthe city.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
