OL,3,CDurham's Milburngate complex sold to
OL,4,Cprivate company
OL,6,F"Beyond entertainment and hospitality,
OL,7,Fthe development addresses Durham's
OL,8,Fgrowing demand for quality urban
OL,9,Fliving and workspace. The development
OL,10,Fincludes office space and 153 built-to-
OL,11,Frent apartments, positioning the city
OL,12,Fcentre as an attractive location for
OL,13,Fboth working professionals and
OL,14,Fresidents seeking contemporary city
OL,15,Fliving."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
