PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773090363
OL,3,CDurham's Milburngate complex sold to
OL,4,Cprivate company
OL,6,FCllr Andrew Husband, Leader of Durham
OL,7,FCounty Council, said: "We welcome the
OL,8,Fnews of the sale of the Milburngate
OL,9,Fdevelopment to a new developer,
OL,10,Fparticularly given that they have
OL,11,Falready set out their intention to
OL,12,Fbring the site to completion and
OL,13,Fensure it is able to fulfil its
OL,14,Fpotential in this prime location at
OL,15,Fthe heart of Durham City.
OL,17,F"We look forward to the development
OL,18,Fbeing completed as soon as possible
OL,19,Fand contributing to our exciting plans
OL,20,Ffor the wider Durham Innovation
OL,21,FDistrict in the city centre."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/4
